data.description: REDUCED PRICE!!!!!Stunning two story house with new AC, freshly painted inside and brand new carpet. Located in Lake Nona Beautiful Golf community Eagle Creek with 24 hours security guards. It offers Championship golf course, pro shop, restaurant, lounge, resort style club house, pools, fitness center, play ground, tennis and basketball courts. Close to Lake Nona medical city, UCF medical school, VA hospital, Nemours hospital, Valencia college, shopping, restaurants. and major roads. Great schools. The house feature includes 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, split floor plan, high ceiling large family room with tiles, plus front living room and upstairs loft. Master suite downstairs. open kitchen with upgrade 42" wood cabinets, separate dining room. separate laundry room. double paver drive way. Complete water filter system providing filtered water to the whole house, drinking, shower and laundry
